sequenceDiagram
    participant Angular as Angular App
    participant Browser as Browser
    participant BearerFilter as BearerTokenFilter
    participant SessionFilter as SessionFilter
    participant AuthCtrl as AuthController
    participant SessionSvc as SessionService
    participant SessionRepo as SessionRepository
    participant H2 as H2 Database
    
    Note over Angular: User clicks "Get Sessions"
    Angular->>Angular: Get bearerToken from storage
    Angular->>Browser: GET /api/auth/sessions<br/>Authorization: Bearer {JWT token}
    
    Browser->>BearerFilter: HTTP Request intercepted
    Note over BearerFilter: Extract JWT from<br/>Authorization Header
    BearerFilter->>BearerFilter: Validate JWT signature<br/>Check expiration<br/>Extract userId & email
    BearerFilter->>BearerFilter: Set request attribute<br/>userId = decoded value<br/>userEmail = decoded value
    
    Browser->>SessionFilter: Next Filter
    Note over SessionFilter: Extract sessionId from<br/>PINGSSO_SESSION cookie
    SessionFilter->>SessionFilter: Set request attribute<br/>sessionId = cookie value
    
    SessionFilter->>AuthCtrl: Forward Authenticated Request
    
    AuthCtrl->>AuthCtrl: Get userId from<br/>request.getAttribute("userId")
    AuthCtrl->>AuthCtrl: Verify userId is not null
    
    opt Unauthorized Check
        AuthCtrl->>AuthCtrl: If userId == null
        AuthCtrl-->>Browser: HTTP 401<br/>{error: "Unauthorized"}
    end
    
    AuthCtrl->>SessionSvc: getActiveSessionsForUser(userId)
    SessionSvc->>SessionRepo: findByUserIdAndActive(userId, true)
    SessionRepo->>H2: SELECT * FROM sessions<br/>WHERE user_id = ? AND active = true
    H2-->>SessionRepo: List<Session>
    SessionRepo-->>SessionSvc: Sessions List
    SessionSvc-->>AuthCtrl: Active Sessions
    
    AuthCtrl->>AuthCtrl: Build Response<br/>{<br/>  success: true,<br/>  sessions: [...],<br/>  count: N<br/>}
    
    AuthCtrl-->>Browser: HTTP 200 OK
    Browser-->>Angular: Response with Sessions
    Angular->>Angular: Display sessions<br/>in UI
